---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="py-32 px-6 bg-[#1A1C2C] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-center mb-24 tracking-tighter uppercase">
            Sabemos lo que se siente...
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-white group-hover:text-[#1A1C2C] transition-all duration-500"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:thermometer-alert" class="w-10 h-10" />
                </div>
                <p class="text-xl font-light italic leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                    "¿Masa sobrefermentada por el calor? Pizzametrics ajusta los tiempos por ti."
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-white group-hover:text-[#1A1C2C] transition-all duration-500"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:scale-balance" class="w-10 h-10" />
                </div>
                <p class="text-xl font-light italic leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                    "¿Luchando con los porcentajes del panadero? Nosotros hacemos los números, tú
                    haces el arte."
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div
                    class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-white group-hover:text-[#1A1C2C] transition-all duration-500"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:alert-decagram-outline" class="w-10 h-10" />
                </div>
                <p class="text-xl font-light italic leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                    "¿Te quedaste sin harina? La sección 'Pantry' te avisa antes de que empieces a
                    amasar."
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
